#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ", and feel free to"
msgstr ", in se lahko svobodno"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. After placing your orders, look at our Kitchen Display. Click the "
"\"Backend\" menu in the right corner to return to your backend, then switch "
"to the Kitchen Display App."
msgstr ""
"1. Ko oddate naročilo, si oglejte našo razstavo kuhinjskih pripomočkov. Za "
"vrnitev v razstavo kliknite meni »Zaledni del« v desnem kotu in nato "
"preklopite na aplikacijo Kuhinjski prikazovalnik."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. First, create all your employees in the database. Navigate to the "
"Employee App to do so."
msgstr ""
"1. Najprej ustvarite vse zaposlene v zbirki podatkov. To storite v "
"aplikaciji Zaposleni."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Point of sale"
msgstr "1. Prodajno mesto"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. You are ready to welcome your first customers. To do so, select a table "
"on the floor map and select the products they asked for from the list."
msgstr ""
"1. Pripravljeni ste sprejeti svoje prve stranke. To storite tako, da na "
"tlorisu izberete mizo in s seznama izberete izdelke, ki so jih stranke "
"zahtevale."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "2. Create your employees' roles under the \"Work Information\" tab. Some "
#| "are already created for this demo."
msgid ""
"2. Create your employees' roles under the \"Settings\" tab. Some are already "
"created for this demo."
msgstr ""
"2. Vloge svojih zaposlenih ustvarite na zavihku »Informacije o delu«. "
"Nekatere so za to predstavitev že ustvarjene."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Kiosks and self-ordering"
msgstr "2. Kioski in samonaročanje"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. Open your preparation screen. Your orders are there. You can now mark "
"them as done either line by line or the entire order by clicking on the top."
msgstr ""
"2. Odprite zaslon za pripravo. Vaša naročila so tam. Zdaj jih lahko označite "
"kot opravljena po vrsticah ali celotno naročilo s klikom na vrh."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. To make it more interesting, feel free to create a second order. For this "
"one, select the \"Burger Menu Combo\" product. You can choose 2 burger "
"options burger options and 4 different drinks. This \"Combo\" feature will "
"allow you to create a menu with several courses and choices for each."
msgstr ""
"2. Za bolj zanimivo naročilo lahko ustvarite še eno naročilo. Za to izberite "
"izdelek »Kombinacija burger menija«. Izberete lahko 2 možnosti burgerja in 4 "
"različne pijače. Ta funkcija »Kombinacija« vam bo omogočila, da ustvarite "
"meni z več hodi in možnostmi za vsako."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. If you select Max Frite as a customer for your order, you can see that "
"there is a Loyalty Program running on your Point of Sale. Every money spent "
"provide a loyalty point, and 200 loyalty points give access to a free Combo "
"Menu."
msgstr ""
"3. Če za stranko za svoje naročilo izberete Max Frite, lahko vidite, da na "
"vašem prodajnem mestu deluje program zvestobe. Vsak porabljen denar prinese "
"točko zvestobe, 200 točk zvestobe pa omogoča dostop do brezplačnega "
"kombiniranega menija."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Odoo provides your an order status display to let your customer see when "
"their order is ready. It is automatically setup and available by clicking "
"the \"Order status screen\" button on the preparation display."
msgstr ""
"3. Odoo vam ponuja prikaz stanja naročila, da vaša stranka vidi, kdaj je "
"njeno naročilo pripravljeno. Nastavi se samodejno in je na voljo s klikom na "
"gumb »Zaslon s stanjem naročila« na zaslonu priprave."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Preparation displays"
msgstr "3. Pripravljalni zasloni"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Return to the Planning App. You can see a few shifts ready to be planned. "
"Select the down arrow next to the publish button and click \"Auto Plan.\" "
"Your shifts will be automatically assigned based on your employees' "
"availability."
msgstr ""
"3. Vrnite se v aplikacijo za načrtovanje. Vidite lahko nekaj izmen, ki so "
"pripravljene za načrtovanje. Izberite puščico navzdol poleg gumba za objavo "
"in kliknite »Samodejno načrtovanje«. Vaše izmene bodo samodejno dodeljene "
"glede na razpoložljivost vaših zaposlenih."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Replenishment"
msgstr "4. Dopolnitev"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. You can still reassign any shift to adapt the planning."
msgstr ""
"4. Še vedno lahko prerazporedite katero koli izmeno, da prilagodite "
"načrtovanje."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Once you are happy with it, send it to your co-workers by smashing the "
"publish button."
msgstr ""
"5. Ko ste z rezultatom zadovoljni, ga pošljite sodelavcem tako, da "
"pritisnete gumb za objavo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "5. Plan your services"
msgstr "5. Načrtujte svoje storitve"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">⚠️</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">⚠️</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🎉</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🎉</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">💡</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">💡</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🔁</i>"
msgstr "<i class=\"o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal\">🔁</i>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
