#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong>Fast Food Restaurant</strong></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong>Restavracija s hitro prehrano</strong></"
"span>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Ali želite iti še dlje?</strong></span>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>1. Flow 1:</strong> Most products need a human assessment as the "
"remaining quantity cannot be automatically computed. For those: Go to your "
"Purchase App to easily create Requests for Proposal or Purchase Orders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. Tok 1:</strong> Večina izdelkov potrebuje človeško oceno, saj "
"preostale količine ni mogoče samodejno izračunati. Za te: Pojdite v svojo "
"aplikacijo za nakupe, da preprosto ustvarite zahteve za ponudbo ali "
"naročilnice."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>2. Flow 2:</strong> For products that can be tracked, such as "
"bottled beers and sodas, you can use automated purchases. To try it, "
"navigate to your Point of Sale and sell a Blond Beer to a customer."
msgstr ""
"<strong>2. Tok 2:</strong> Za izdelke, ki jih je mogoče slediti, kot so "
"ustekleničena piva in gazirane pijače, lahko uporabite avtomatizirane "
"nakupe. Če želite to preizkusiti, se pomaknite do svoje prodajne točke in "
"stranki prodajte svetlo pivo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h1-fs\">Use case:</span></strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"h1-fs\">Primer uporabe:</span></strong>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Basics:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Osnove:</strong>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Kiosks</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Kioski</strong>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Self-ordering</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Samostojno naročanje</strong>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At the end of your service, remember to close your register. To do so, in "
"the Point of Sale App, select \"Close Register\" in the top-right menu. You "
"can then precise your cash amount and validate the closing."
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu storitve ne pozabite zapreti blagajne. To storite tako, da v "
"aplikaciji Point of Sale v zgornjem desnem meniju izberete »Zapri blagajno«. "
"Nato lahko natančno določite znesek gotovine in potrdite zaključek."

