msgstr "S tem vam bo na zalogi ostalo le še 23 piv."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products, a point of sale configuration and a sample planning."
msgstr ""
"Z nalaganjem predstavitvenih podatkov tega modula je bila vaša baza podatkov "
"napolnjena z nekaj izdelki, konfiguracijo prodajnega mesta in vzorčnim "
"načrtovanjem."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_4
msgid "Cash (Restaurant)"
msgstr "Gotovina (Restavracija)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_56_product_template
msgid "Cheese 250gr"
msgstr "Sir 250 g"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a stunning <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">website</font></"
"strong> and start receiving orders directly in Odoo. Go live with your "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few "
"minutes."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite osupljivo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">spletno stran</"
"font></strong> in začnite prejemati naročila neposredno v Odooju. Zaženite "
"svojo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Spletno trgovino</font></"
"strong> v nekaj minutah."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Odkrijte več o Odoo-ju tako, da se poglobite v našo"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Odkrijte osnove tega paketa in raziščite vse možnosti, ki jih Odoo ponuja za "
"izboljšanje vaše izkušnje."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't forget to hit the \"Order\" button each time you change an order. This "
"will forward the order to the Kitchen Display."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite vsakič, ko spremenite naročilo, klikniti gumb »Naročilo«. S tem "
"se bo naročilo posredovalo v kuhinjski zaslon."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Each order will be sent to your preparation displays and if you don't "
"configure a payment terminal for each, they can pay directly online."
msgstr ""
"Vsako naročilo bo poslano na vaše pripravljalne zaslone in če za vsako ne "
"konfigurirate plačilnega terminala, lahko plačajo neposredno prek spleta."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.program,name:fast_food.loyalty_program_2
msgid "Foodie Card"
msgstr "Kartica za gurmane"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.reward,description:fast_food.loyalty_reward_1
msgid "Free Product - Cheese Burger"
msgstr "Brezplačen izdelek - sirov burger"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the Point of Sale, open your register on the main dashboard."
msgstr "Na prodajnem mestu odprite svojo blagajno na glavni nadzorni plošči."

#. module: fast_food
