msgstr "Živjo!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your Purchase App, you can see a new Purchase Order that "
"is ready to be sent. You can choose a packaging if your product has an "
"existing one."
msgstr ""
"Če odprete aplikacijo za nakupe, lahko vidite novo naročilnico, ki je "
"pripravljena za pošiljanje. Izberete lahko embalažo, če ima vaš izdelek "
"obstoječo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to assign them an Odoo user account, you can select a related "
#| "user in the \"HR Settings\" tab."
msgid ""
"If you want to assign them an Odoo user account, you can select a related "
"user in the same \"Settings\" tab."
msgstr ""
"Če jim želite dodeliti uporabniški račun Odoo, lahko na zavihku »Nastavitve "
"kadrovske službe« izberete povezanega uporabnika."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case. (In the next Knowledge Article)"
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti praktični voden ogled tega modula, uvozite predstavitvene "
"podatke in preizkusite primer uporabe. (V naslednjem članku znanja)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_57_product_template
msgid "Ketchup 500ml"
msgstr "Kečap 500ml"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:planning.role,name:fast_food.planning_role_3
msgid "Kitchen"
msgstr "Kuhinja"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.program,portal_point_name:fast_food.loyalty_program_2
msgid "Loyalty point(s)"
msgstr "Točke zvestobe"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Make them pay the orders to release the table and continue your service."
msgstr "Naj plačajo naročila, da sprostijo mizo in nadaljujejo s postrežbo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage Loyalty Programs and many other kind of promotions, gifts and coupons "
"in the related page in your Point of Sales App &gt; Products."
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte programe zvestobe in številne druge vrste promocij, daril in "
"kuponov na ustrezni strani v vašem Prodajnem mestu &gt; in aplikaciji "
"Izdelki."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte vse svoje komunikacijske kanale na enem mestu z Odoojem "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Avtomatizacija trženja</font></"
"strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-poštno trženje</font></"
"strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Trženje na družbenih "
"omrežjih</font></strong>, in<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS "
"Trženje</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage recurring tasks and never forget any replenishment or cleaning with "
"the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte ponavljajoča se opravila in nikoli ne pozabite na dolivanje "
"zalog ali čiščenje z <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Aplikacijo "
"Project</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte svoje računovodstvo lažje kot kdaj koli prej s popolnoma "
"integriranim okoljem. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Računovodska "
"aplikacija\n"
"</font></strong>)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo also provides easy self ordering possibilities. Print a specific QR "
"code for each table on your Point of Sale settings and allow your customer "
"to order directly on their mobile phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ponuja tudi preproste možnosti samostojnega naročanja. V nastavitvah "
"prodajnega mesta natisnite posebno kodo QR za vsako mizo in omogočite "
"strankam, da naročijo neposredno na svojem mobilnem telefonu."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo je v celoti integriran v aplikacijo. Prenesite jo in svoj telefon "
"spremenite v dodatno blagajno (in še veliko več)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as :"
msgstr "Odoo vam ponuja neskončne možnosti, kot so:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Seveda je to le pregled funkcij, ki so vključene v ta paket. Dodajate lahko "
"nove aplikacije, brišete/spreminjate demo podatke in preizkušate vse!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izdelki tam, lahko kliknete pametni gumb »Potrdilo«, da potrdite "
"potrdilo in dodate te nove izdelke na zalogo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_2
msgid "Online Payment"
msgstr "Plačilo preko spleta"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your customers easily with the<strong> "
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Organizirajte svoje dogodke in se enostavno povežite s strankami z\n"
"<strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Aplikacijo za Dogodke\n"
"</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Plan your services easily using the Planning App."
msgstr "Z aplikacijo za Načrtovanje preprosto načrtujte svoje storitve."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontaktirajte nas"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are displayed in the smart buttons on top of your product. "
"You can see a minimum quantity, and a maximum. Each time the forecast stock "
"lowers beneath the minimum stock, it automatically creates a purchase order "
"to replenish to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za ponovno naročanje so prikazana v pametnih gumbih na vrhu vašega "
"izdelka. Vidite lahko minimalno in maksimalno količino. Vsakič, ko "
"napovedane zaloge padejo pod minimalno zalogo, se samodejno ustvari naročilo "
"za dopolnitev do maksimalne količine."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Replenishment is essential but challenging for a bar owner to systematize."
msgstr ""
"Dopolnjevanje zalog je bistveno, vendar za lastnika bara zahtevno, da ga "
"sistematizira."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_58_product_template
msgid "Sanitizer 250ml"
msgstr "Razkužilo 250ml"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:planning.role,name:fast_food.planning_role_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Storitev"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_1
msgid "Sodexo Card Payment"
msgstr "Sodexo Plačilo s kartico"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kitchen Displays</font></strong> "
"will ensure a great follow-up of every order in your bar and kitchen."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kuhinjski zasloni</font></strong> "
"bodo zagotovili odlično spremljanje vsakega naročila v vašem baru in kuhinji."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The kiosk layout is optimized for vertical usage, as most booths use that "
"kind of display."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev kioska je optimizirana za vertikalno uporabo, saj večina kabin "
"uporablja tovrstni prikazovalnik."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The stock is only updated when you close your register. Let's do it before "
"continuing to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Zaloga se posodobi šele, ko zaprete blagajno. Naredimo to, preden "
"nadaljujemo z naslednjim korakom."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr "Vse to je brezplačno v vaši trenutni naročnini; kar raziščite! 🙃"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory App</font></strong> "
"to manage your stock and receive products."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Aplikacijo za inventar\n"
"</font></strong> za upravljanje zalog in prejemanje izdelkov."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning App</font></strong> "
"to schedule and share your shifts with your employees."
msgstr ""
"Z aplikacijo za<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Načrtovanje</font></"
"strong> lahko načrtujete in delite svoje izmene z zaposlenimi."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale</font></strong> "
"at the desk for your sales. You can also download the Odoo Mobile App on any "
"phone to take orders. And create <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Kiosks </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">or QR Codes</span></font></strong> to ensure self-ordering."
msgstr ""
"Za prodajo uporabite <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Prodajno mesto</"
"font></strong> na mizi. Za sprejemanje naročil lahko prenesete tudi mobilno "
"aplikacijo Odoo na katerikoli telefon. Za samostojno naročanje lahko "
"ustvarite <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kioske</font><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">ali QR kode.</"
"span></font></strong>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"to reorder your products."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Nabavno aplikacijo</font></"
"strong> za ponovno naročanje izdelkov."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:fast_food.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Dobrodošli! Veselo raziskovanje."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "Bi se radi z nami pogovorili o svoji nastavitvi Odoo ali šli še dlje?"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Do vsake nameščene aplikacije v vaši bazi podatkov Odoo lahko dostopate na "
"glavni nadzorni plošči."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit the floor map by clicking \"Edit plan\" in the top-right "
"menu when on the table selection step of your Point of Sale."
msgstr ""
"Tloris lahko preprosto uredite tako, da v zgornjem desnem meniju kliknete "
"»Uredi načrt«, ko ste na koraku izbire mize na vašem prodajnem mestu."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now email your Request for Proposal to your vendor or confirm it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko svojo zahtevo za ponudbo pošljete dobavitelju po e-pošti ali pa "
"jo potrdite ročno."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that there is a reordering rule configured for this product if "
"you go to Inventory &gt; Products &gt; Blond Beer"
msgstr ""
"Če odprete Zalogo, lahko vidite, da je za ta izdelek konfigurirano pravilo "
"za ponovno naročanje &gt; Izdelki &gt; Svetlo Pivo"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Zaključili ste ta primer uporabe za demonstracijo! Obstaja na milijone "
"drugih načinov, kako prilagoditi svojo Odoo nastavitev svojim poslovnim "
"potrebam."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You currently have two steps in your Kitchen Displays: one for the kitchen/"
"bar and one for the service. You can configure steps in the kitchen display "
"configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno imate v kuhinjskih prikazih dva koraka: enega za kuhinjo/bar in "
"enega za postrežbo. Korake lahko konfigurirate v meniju za konfiguracijo "
"kuhinjskega prikaza."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Fast Food Restaurant package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"Niste uvozili predstavitvenih podatkov? Še vedno lahko uvozite. Pojdite v "
"Aplikacije &gt; Industrije &gt; Nadgradite svoj paket za restavracijo s "
"hitro prehrano in označite ustrezno polje."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have two main possibilities in Odoo to ease your replenishment process."
msgstr ""
"V Odooju imate dve glavni možnosti za poenostavitev postopka dopolnjevanja."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Fast Food Restaurant package. By doing so, "
"we have installed many necessary apps to run your restaurant efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Pravkar ste namestili paket Odoo za restavracije s hitro prehrano. S tem smo "
"namestili številne potrebne aplikacije za učinkovito delovanje vaše "
"restavracije."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various actions you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled različnih dejanj, ki jih lahko hitro izvedete s tem paketom z "
"uporabo Odooja, bi morali biti sposobni izvesti naslednje poteke."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your demo database comes with a kiosk to allow your customer to take orders "
"on your booths. Go to the Point of Sale App and select your kiosk to see how "
"it looks and try it!"
msgstr ""
"Vaša demo baza podatkov je opremljena s kioskom, ki strankam omogoča "
"sprejemanje naročil na vaših stojnicah. Pojdite v aplikacijo Prodajno mesto "
"in izberite svoj Kiosk, da si ogledate, kako izgleda, in ga preizkusite!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your orders will automatically move from a step to another while you move it "
"on your preparation display."
msgstr ""
"Vaša naročila se bodo samodejno premaknila iz enega koraka v drugega, ko jih "
"boste premikali na zaslonu za pripravo."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "academy"
msgstr "akademija"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "and"
msgstr "in"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "documentation"
msgstr "dokumentacija"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "if you need help! <br/>"
msgstr "če potrebujete pomoč! <br/>"

